{"name":"Terrify","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Turning an eldritch key, the psyker unlocks his target&rsquo;s deepest and strongest fears, exposing him to the worst recesses of his own psyche. These nightmarish visions are enough to drive even the strongest helplessly mad.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Inflict nightmarish visions on target","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Fellowship 45","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>Slithering deep into the mind of his victim, the psyker unearths their greatest failings, greatest weaknesses, and greatest fears. Using these as tools against his opponent, the psyker can turn even the most courageous warriors into pathetic, whimpering cowards before him. The psyker nominates a single target in range and line of sight who opposes this power with a Willpower test.</p>\n<p>If the target fails to resist the power, it must roll on Table 8&ndash;11: Shock on page 287, adding +10 times the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating to the roll in place of the normal addition for degrees of failure, and immediately apply the effects.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/suspicious.svg","effects":[],"_id":"BTn6VCKrVti0RSxw"}
{"name":"Erasure","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>With a surgeon&rsquo;s skill, the psyker opens up his target&rsquo;s mind and slices away a memory, removing it forever. This power is of immense utility to an Inquisitor&rsquo;s work, particularly one who wishes to operate discreetly, without the usual mess of an execution.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Remove a memory from targetâ€™s mind","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Fellowship 40","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"5*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker chooses a single foe in range and line of sight who opposes this power with a Willpower test. If he fails, the psyker removes a memory of a recent event from the target&rsquo;s mind. The psyker can only remove an amount of time from the target&rsquo;s memory up to 10 x PR minutes, and the event removed cannot have occurred more than PR hours prior to the use of this power. The enemy is left with a gap in his memory, with no recollection of what occurred during that time.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/suspicious.svg","effects":[],"_id":"DyHY7GKlouFLAFSE"}
{"name":"Dominate","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Demonstrating the superiority of his mutant mind, the telepath subverts his foe&rsquo;s will and forces him to act against his every inclination. Few psychic abilities are so rightly feared.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Force target to follow a single command","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 40","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"5*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker nominates a number targets in range and line of sight up to half his psy rating (rounded up) who oppose this power with a Willpower test. Each target that fails to resist the power must follow a simple command given by the psyker. Some example orders include &ldquo;Flee,&rdquo; &ldquo;Fall,&rdquo; or &ldquo;Attack your friend.&rdquo; If the command is a potentially suicidal act, each target receives a +20 to its Willpower test to Oppose the power. In all cases, the command must be achievable in a single round.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/suspicious.svg","effects":[],"_id":"R5T6NPlOkBdVejER"}
{"name":"Telepathic Link","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>In this, the simplest yet purest expression of his powers, the telepath establishes a mental connection to another, linking their minds and allowing him to receive or transmit thoughts. When stealth is essential, such silent communication is ideal.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Create a mental connection with target","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Willpower 35","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"20*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker chooses a person in range and line of sight who opposes this power with a Willpower test. If the target fails, the psyker can either read the person&rsquo;s thoughts or send him a brief mental message.</p>\n<p>&bull; Thought Reading: The psyker reads the target&rsquo;s thoughts, with the GM determining the nature of the information gained. The more degrees of success scored on the Focus Power test, the more information is gained overall. The higher the PR of the power, the more secretive the information gained.</p>\n<p>&bull; Thought Sending: The psyker causes a message to appear in the target&rsquo;s mind as if he has just heard it spoken aloud. The message can be no longer than 5 x PR seconds long. If the target of this power is aware of what the psyker is trying to do, he can voluntarily fail the opposed Willpower test, counting as having rolled a 100.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/suspicious.svg","effects":[],"_id":"TTCVi2Db8Y8ZZNOw"}
{"name":"Puppet Master","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>In the ultimate expression of telepathic power, the psyker utterly crushes his target&rsquo;s will, locking him away in a dark corner of his own mind and taking complete control of his body. After recovering their wits, those subjected to this power are often struck with bouts of insecurity, never certain again if their actions are truly their own.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Control the actions of target","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Fellowship 55","action":"Full","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"Special","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker nominates a single target in range and line of sight with total wounds no greater than 3 times the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating, who opposes this power with a Willpower test. If the target fails to resist the power, it is controlled by the psyker like a puppet. For the duration of the power, the psyker can divide his Actions between himself and the target. The dominated target uses its own Characteristics, but at &ndash;10 due to the crudity of the control. If at any point the psyker would make the target perform a potentially suicidal action, the target can attempt a Challenging (+0) Opposed Willpower test to try to break free of the power. Additionally, the power breaks as soon as the target moves out of range.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/suspicious.svg","effects":[],"_id":"TTLWex96ILJumrrm"}
{"name":"Mental Fortitude","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Drawing from the limitless potential of the Warp, the psyker augments the mental abilities of his targets, providing defence against the stresses of combat and the terrors of the galaxy.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Share Adamantium Faith talent with allies","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Adamantium Faith","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"3*PR","sustained":"Free Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>For the duration of this power, a number of allies up to the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating within range count as having the Adamantium Faith talent. Allies affected by this power lose its benefits as soon as they move out of range.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/suspicious.svg","effects":[],"_id":"U49qB57yt1e3GIEu"}
{"name":"Invisibility","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Clouding enemy minds, the psyker obscures his allies from their foes&rsquo; senses. Though eyes and other senses detect them as normal, their minds do not perceive them, save for a slight distortion in their vision.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Obscure targets  from view","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Agility 30, psy rating 4","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":-10,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"Free Action","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker nominates a single target within range and line of sight (this can be the psyker himself). For the duration of the power, the target counts having the Stealth skill at Known (rank 1), and gains a bonus to Stealth tests equal to +5 times the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating. Additionally, all ranged attacks made against the target suffer a penalty equal to &ndash;5 times the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating. If the target moves beyond the power&rsquo;s range, he loses this power&rsquo;s benefits.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/suspicious.svg","effects":[],"_id":"hT6JJaIWK0JZbPEl"}
{"name":"Hallucination","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>The human mind&rsquo;s grasp on reality is fragile and easily manipulated with sufficient power. With his own psychic senses, the telepath touches the psyche of his target and severs its connection to normal existence.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Cause target to suffer uncontrolled visions","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Fellowship 40","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Concentration","effect":"<p>The psyker nominates a single target in range and line of sight who opposes this power with a Willpower test. If the target fails to resist the power, it must roll on Table 5&ndash;3: Hallucinogenic Effects on page 146, and immediately apply the effects. The effect rolled on the table lasts for a number of rounds equal to half the psyker&rsquo;s psy rating, rounded up.</p>","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"energy","formula":"","penetration":"","special":""}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/suspicious.svg","effects":[],"_id":"oLjWASzsdPzY74Bc"}
{"name":"Psychic Shriek","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"psychicPower","data":{"description":"<p>Drawing a deep soul-breath, the psyker unleashes a rippling Warp tide that sears the souls and blasts the minds of those in its path. The violent psychic wave is enough to overwhelm and shut down the minds of those it strikes, while those not slain outright are left reeling and dazed.</p>","source":"","shortDescription":"Attack target with a psychic wave","cost":0,"prerequisite":"Psy rating 3","action":"Half","focusPower":{"difficulty":0,"test":"Willpower"},"range":"10*PR","sustained":"No","subtype":"Attack","effect":"","damage":{"zone":"bolt","type":"explosive","formula":"1d10+2+2*PR","penetration":"","special":"concussive (1)"}},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_resources/icons/PsychicPowers/suspicious.svg","effects":[],"_id":"proEWd3hdiZYdwMR"}
